03/05/2007
WASHINGTON, United States -- Vice President Dick Cheney assured visiting Montenegrin President Filip Vujanovic on Wednesday (May 2nd) that the United States is ready to back Montenegro's aspirations for Euro-Atlantic integration.
They met a day after Vujanovic and Secretary of State Condoleezza Rice sealed the Status of Forces Agreement for enhanced bilateral military co-operation.
Vujanovic is also lobbying for increased US investment in Montenegro.
(Vijesti - 03/05/07;
RTCG, Mina, AP - 02/05/07)
